### Delete a message
DELETE {{api_url}}/conversation_messages/1.json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Update a message
PUT {{api_url}}/conversation_messages/2.json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversation_message": {
